
Given	I'm logged-in with valid credentials
And	I go to Page 07 of Thoracic CT

When I select 'Finding' radio button
Then 'Finding' dropdown menu is enabled

When I select 'Upper abdomen, liver/gall bladder' from the dropdown menu
Then 'Add new finding' button is enabled
And 'Focal liver lesion' checkbox is enabled
And 'Diffuse liver lesion' checkbox is enabled
And 'Cholecystolithiasis' checkbox is enabled
And 'Wall thickening of the gall bladder' checkbox is enabled

When I select 'Focal liver lesion' checkbox
Then 'Right' radio button is enabled
And 'Left' radio button is enabled
And 'Size' input field is enabled
And 'Classification' dropdown menu is enabled
And '> 1 lesion of the same entity' checkbox is enabled

When I select 'Diffuse liver lesion
Then 'Steatosis hepatis' radio button is enabled
And 'Cirrhosis of the liver' radio button is enabled
And 'Hemosiderosis' radio button is enabled

When I select 'Hemosiderosis' radio button
Then 'Suspected' checkbox is enabled
